    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/b83bbc04aaf91314080848ef2a7a97a5.avif?t=1765574655\" width=616 height=90 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/c89d3b5a4c562863967577397fb7bfa6.webp?t=1765574655\" width=616 height=30 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >OnSlaught puts you in the pilot seat of an unending nightmare - where an entire alien civilization wants you <strong>dead</strong>. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll face many enemies, each demanding a unique weapon and strategy to defeat similar to classic boomer shooters like DOOM.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight flesh abominations, slingshot around black holes, and destroy an army of biomechanical alien ships.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/c89d3b5a4c562863967577397fb7bfa6.webp?t=1765574655\" width=616 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/2e48a8a63a4c860e33a5d6eb0f49226f.poster.avif?t=1765574655\" width=559 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/2e48a8a63a4c860e33a5d6eb0f49226f.webm?t=1765574655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/982119a29fae486604c4bfde9b90965f.avif?t=1765574655\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/c89d3b5a4c562863967577397fb7bfa6.webp?t=1765574655\" width=616 height=30 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Almost every asteroid in OnSlaught is fully destructible. </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your grappling hook to fling explosive barrels, asteroids, and space junk at you enemies alongside your 9 other weapons.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/c89d3b5a4c562863967577397fb7bfa6.webp?t=1765574655\" width=616 height=30 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/4d95446a1c95041ff7e86cf9132e6506.poster.avif?t=1765574655\" width=606 height=238 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/4d95446a1c95041ff7e86cf9132e6506.webm?t=1765574655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/6c824806281a41721276817dd143d129.avif?t=1765574655\" width=616 height=90 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/c89d3b5a4c562863967577397fb7bfa6.webp?t=1765574655\" width=616 height=30 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your humanity has been stripped away. Only agony remains.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>M̶a̸k̵e̵ Ĝ̵̟͜͝ö̶̢̤̜́̍d̵̟̰̓ B̴̦̠̘́L̵̰͉͎͌͊͂Ẹ̸̣͋̏̂͜Ė̵̢̑D̶̨͊</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/c89d3b5a4c562863967577397fb7bfa6.webp?t=1765574655\" width=616 height=30 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/c1c53fe89967595f2af2e3bfdb22c832.poster.avif?t=1765574655\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1698820/extras/c1c53fe89967595f2af2e3bfdb22c832.webm?t=1765574655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
